{"date":"2013-10-05","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/e8/98/69484_47lg4.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/e8/98/69484_47lg4.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/e8/98/69484_47lg4.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/e8/98/69484_47lg4.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/e8/98/69484_47lg4.jpg"},"summary":"幼时曾深陷绝望深渊的直枝理树，与4位少年少女相遇了。\r\n在那之后数年，理树作为Little Busters的一员，喧闹地过着快乐的每一天。 \r\n这样的时间能够一直持续就好了。理树所期望的只有这样。 \r\n某日，恭介突然表示要成立一支棒球队伍， 理树则开始了寻找成员的任务。 \r\n在这样的过程中，理树邂逅了新的成员们。 \r\n和大家一起参加试胆大会，潜入女生宿舍时被换上女装，一起演人偶剧……。 \r\n经历了许多快乐的事情， 同时也在大家的帮助下解决了各自拥有的烦恼。 \r\n最后在棒球比赛中，理树确认了和最好的朋友们之间的牵绊。 \r\n——然而，这并不是结束。 \r\n和来谷唯湖之间的故事。 \r\n理树与铃的故事。 \r\n以及，理树和铃终于知晓的“世界的秘密”。 \r\nLittle Busters真正的物语，自此开始——。","name":"リトルバスターズ! 〜Refrain〜","name_cn":"Little Busters! 〜Refrain〜","tags":[{"name":"key","count":1213,"total_cont":0},{"name":"J.C.STAFF","count":1139,"total_cont":0},{"name":"麻枝准","count":804,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL改","count":727,"total_cont":0},{"name":"催泪","count":664,"total_cont":0},{"name":"LittleBusters！","count":610,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2013年10月","count":558,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":487,"total_cont":0},{"name":"校园","count":374,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改","count":328,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2013","count":268,"total_cont":0},{"name":"世界的秘密","count":257,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":214,"total_cont":0},{"name":"第二季","count":107,"total_cont":0},{"name":"友情","count":60,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":42,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":41,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山川吉樹","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"续作","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Little.Busters","count":24,"total_cont":0},{"name":"LB","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山川吉树","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"青春","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"key社","count":16,"total_c